'''Senior Administrative Aide''',<ref name="HC 22" /> also known as '''administrator''',<ref name="Vader 10" /> was a title held by the [[Umbaran]] [[Sly Moore]], the [[Chief of Staff]] to [[Supreme Chancellor]] of the [[Galactic Republic]] [[Darth Sidious|Sheev Palpatine]].<ref name="HC 22" /> Moore continued to use the title when she served the Republic's successor, the [[Galactic Empire]]. Under the Empire, Senior Administrative Aide Moore was able to direct [[Imperial Military]] forces on special order from [[Galactic Emperor]] Palpatine.<ref name="Vader 10" />

